text: Nicolas Constant (8 March 1886 - 10 November 1971) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1886 births Category:1971 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nord (French department)
